FBIS4-38317 "drsov104_d_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-104 Daily Report 28 May 1994 Regional Affairs Interior Minister Killed in Explosion Interior Minister Killed in Explosion LD2805111094 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 1000 GMT 28 May 94 LD2805111094 Moscow Russian Television Network Russian BFN [From the "Vesti" newscast] [Text] INTERFAX has reported that Chechen Interior Minister Magomet Eldiyev, his deputy Said Alibatayev, and their driver were killed in a car crash on the night of 27 May. According to unconfirmed reports, the minister's car exploded on a mine 20 km west of Groznyy.
